ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: The impact of the content of the message.

ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: A coded identifier of a supported messaging event.

ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: Guidance on how this event is handled, such as internal system trigger points, business rules, etc.

ivardefs.name: focus
ivardefs.desc: A resource associated with the event.  This is the resource that defines the event.

ivardefs.name: mode
ivardefs.desc: The mode of this event declaration - whether an application is a sender or receiver.

ivardefs.name: request
ivardefs.desc: Information about the request for this event.

ivardefs.name: response
ivardefs.desc: Information about the response for this event.

properties.desc: A description of the solution's support for an event at this end-point.
